Within which directory will you find the repositories used by yum?
A)  /etc/yum.conf
B)  /etc/repos
C)  /etc/yum.conf.d
D)  /etc/yum.repos.d
D
D. Configuration files related to the repositories for yum are located in /etc/yum.repos.d. Of the other options, /etc/yum.conf is a file and not a directory, and theother directories do not exist.
